feat: oracle (#1082)

Add Oracle script;
This implementation works through MultiSig contract.
For prevent races it have two modes:

    In master mode script submitting price change to multisig
    In slave mode script listen submitting from master, verify price, and confirm it.

Any mode script have price watcher, for timely update SNM-USD price.
Watcher loads data from cmc SNM ticker.
